gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Grizzlies 109, Wizards 97
gameRecap.excerpt: The Grizzlies defeated the Wizards, 109-97. Trey Jemison notched a career-high 24 points, along with six rebounds for the Grizzlies, while GG Jackson (19 points) and Jake LaRavia (16 points) added a combined 35 points in the victory. Kyle Kuzma tallied 24 points, seven rebounds and five assists for the Wizards in the losing effort. The Grizzlies improve to 23-43 on the season, while the Wizards fall to 11-54.
